entries.journal_entry_description: During her patrols, Tala'oree has come across a pack of hostile Uwari Beetles that seem to be bent on destroying the Luilris Gardens. She wants to kill 6 of them.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Tala'oree has sent you to destroy 6 pesky Uwari Beetles. You can find them near the surface of the Myyydril Caverns.
